6. Troubleshooting and common fixes (step-by-step)
- Vitest no tests found:
  1. Confirm test files exist under tests/unit/ and end with .test.js
  2. Run vitest --run tests/unit/*.test.js locally to reproduce
- Node version mismatch:
  1. Use nvm or install Node 24+ in CI matrix
  2. Confirm node --version in CI before running npm scripts
- agentic-lib workflow path errors:
  1. Verify agentic-lib.toml [paths] values match repository layout
  2. If automation writes to sandbox, check CONTRIBUTING.md sandbox mappings

